The paper discusses a new algorithm for reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The algorithm involves principles of exploration and imitation learning, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the potential application of the algorithm in robotics (cs.RO), which is another subfield of AI. The algorithm is tested on Atari games, which are often used as benchmarks in computer vision (cs.CV) and game theory (cs.GT) research.
